name: SUNHUNTER #1 WHEN 3000 Sunsets meet AI
description: SUNHUNTER is the fruit of Human & Machine collaboration. 2800 photos, taken over the last fifteen years, all over the world (Europe, Middle East, America, Asia), have been used to train a machine learning algorithm to produce this unbelievable landscape. SUNHUNTER is the result of many years of sunsets and sunrise hunting. it is the peaceful moment between night and day, and night... between light, and darkness, between life and death. It is the beginning and the end of everything
